repository.name: Free_CyberSecurity_Professional_Development_Resources
repository.description: An awesome list of FREE resources for training, conferences, speaking, labs, reading, etc that are free. Originally built during COVID-19 for cybersecurity professionals with downtime can take advantage of to improve their skills and marketability to come out on the other side ready to rock. Now its taken on a life of its own and will persist, COVID be damned.

development_potential.assessment: Excellent potential for integration. High community engagement with 1965 stars and active development. Consider for immediate evaluation.
